ARTIFICIAL EXISTENCE is finally here! Swipe through for a sneak preview →

We started this film back in 2017 and it has made quite the journey around the world, snagging some pretty amazing festival wins along the way 👏🏼 We are so excited to finally share it with you exclusively on @filmshortage 

Thank you to everyone involved who had a hand in bringing this world to life, and especially to @j.d.marshall for allowing me to be your Evelyn.

LINK IN BIO to watch now!! 👽 

Artificial Existence

Friends!!! I need your help ☺️

I have graciously been invited by @arthurmurraypgh to compete in a wonderful charity event on 10/20 called Dancing For a Cause

This event benefits @watchfulshepusa — who do some incredible work in preventing child abuse. If you’re in Pittsburgh, come get dressed up real fancy like and come out to support a great cause! There will be dancing, dancing, and more dancing 💃🏻 Plus I will be performing to try to snag that coveted trophy 🏆 

Even if you can’t make it, please consider donating to support this incredible non-profit, and don’t forget to cast a vote for moi while you’re at it! If you work for a big company, get them to donate and buy a round of seats for ya 😉 

To entice you even more, I’ve included a video of @lopezc2011 and I “practicing”

CHA CHA CHA

Link in my bio to donate or get tickets!! 🎟️💃🏻🏆

lots of bruises, but way more healing ✨

this latest chapter has been my favorite of them all; overflowing with gratitude for my sisters and soulmates who were there with me through times of hardship, the guidance and wisdom and truths that we discovered together, the incredible places traveled to and explored, the fears conquered, risks taken, and for the profoundly magical soul-shattering moments that have come my way lately ❤️‍🔥 I do not take one second of this crazy beautiful life for granted.
